{"tid":2434030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長者信專家呼籲　打針死亡　專家委員會：病人自己走入去接種疫苗","createTime":"2021-03-05T09:10:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T13:55:18.000Z","uid":261647,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e041011eebe6d06a19ad5fdab4e48c89153879c4","tid":2434030,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T09:10:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/benson.tsang/posts/10158568387809934\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbenson.tsang%2Fposts%2F10158568387809934&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=d9c2c949\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/benson.tsang/posts/10158568387809934</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRH9Cjv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRH9Cjv.jpg&h=c8997752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：Benson Tsang<br />\n<br />\n在這個荒誕事情不斷發生的香港，堅持每一天仍然睇新聞，就係要睇清睇楚香港敗壞淪喪到怎樣的階段。一班疫苗專家委員會成員，每次企出嚟都講一啲荒謬絕倫的說話，簡直令人髮指！<br />\n<br />\n就像昨天，呢位專家其中這一句話，聽到佢講完之後我真係對住電視「屌」咗一聲，連我溫和到不得了的老婆，聽到之後都在廁所走出來同我鬧埋一份！<br />\n<br />\n長者相信你哋班「專家」呼籲去打針，出咗事未有驗屍報告就將責任推落死者「有責任了解自己身體狀況」，仲賤格到話係「病人自己去打」！🤬🤬🤬🤬🤬<br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以講俾我知：「病人自己走入去接種疫苗」這句說話的，你所理解的「潛台詞」係咩意思！"},{"pid":"ebc0c67eb223aa177dde593f2b293feadc23f8f4","tid":2434030,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T09:13:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/05ba6dX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F05ba6dX.png&h=2e31d785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/Benson_Tsang\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2FBenson_Tsang&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=876c1331\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/Benson_Tsang</a>"},{"pid":"34c8dab0fa59af5c7bfcc8814ae9d3b3c2f9fb47","tid":2434030,"uid":40932,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTi